# Akshi
> Local-first software you build by describing it — apps as data, not code, that run on your devices and answer only to your keys.
This is the **build repo**. The product story lives in [`docs/About.md`](docs/About.md); the bet, the world, and the falsification clauses live in [`docs/Vision.md`](docs/Vision.md).
## Where things are
| For | Read |
|---|---|
| What Akshi is | [docs/About.md](docs/About.md) · [docs/Vision.md](docs/Vision.md) |
| The plan | [docs/Playbook.md](docs/Playbook.md) — gates, dashboard, pre-committed triggers |
